        "modelVersion": "ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2",
        "description": "ANSYS CFX 15 solver configuration used for all hemolysis validation runs. Mesh: polyhedral, 4.2M cells, y+ < 2 throughout impeller passage. Turbulence model: SST k-omega with low-Reynolds-number correction. Hemolysis sub-model: Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law correlation integrated along pathlines. Boundary conditions: mass-flow inlet, static-pressure outlet, no-slip rotating walls at specified RPM. This configuration corresponds to the internal release candidate build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which preceded the production release by three days. The delta between rc2 and the production build is limited to a PDF release note update and a cosmetic change in the post-processing GUI; solver binaries are byte-identical according to the internal build manifest."
